data.description: 365 REASONS to buy!!!  Discover one daily in this 4 Bedroom 2Story home in exciting location close hospital, schools, shopping and easy highway access.  Seller has updated bathrooms with new marble floors, faucets, sinks, and shower doors.  New granite in kitchen plus new dishwasher, range and dishwasher plus faucet.  Basement is almost finished - seller has insulated it - put in a NOVA system and roughed in for bath and new Hot Water Heater.  New fans in all the bedrooms - upstairs laundry with new floor and stationary tub.  On top of that a new Generac generator.  Watch the seasons change on your all-new composite deck - Don't miss a single day of pleasure in this amazing 2 story waiting for you.  Call now before the sunsets.
